latestChanges.title: Reviewed
latestChanges.body: A literature search was conducted in March 2016 to identify evidence-based guidelines, UK policy, systematic reviews, and key randomized controlled trials published since the last revision of the topic. No major changes to clinical recommendations have been made, although minor restructuring of the topic has been undertaken.
